snippet.title: Run Sausage Run - Xbox One Gameplay
snippet.description:
CrazyLabs, owned by DECA (as part of Embracer Group), originally made this for iOS and Android. Apparently it was popular enough for CrazyLabs to team up with QubicGames to port the game to PC and consoles... and it was a surprise hit, believe it or not.

Sausage Run / Run Sausage Run (C) CrazyLabs, DECA Games
Also available on Steam, iOS, Android and Nintendo Switch
